  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a alsa-oss</title>

    <para>
      The <application>alsa-oss</application> package contains the alsa-oss
compatibility library. This is used by programs which wish to use the
alsa-oss sound interface.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

